# yql_proto_scheme

Tool for creating a proto schema parser for YQL.

https://yql.yandex-team.ru/docs/yt/misc/schema#_yql_proto_field

## Usage
```
$ /usr/lib/yandex/yql_proto_scheme --help
usage: yql_proto_scheme [-h] path message

positional arguments:
  path        Path to proto file
  message     Name of proto Message

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
```


## Usage example
```
~$ /usr/lib/yandex/yql_proto_scheme market.proto.ir.UltraController.proto Offer
$config_Offer = AsAtom(@@{"name": "Market.UltraControllerServiceData.Offer", "meta": "", "format": "protobin", "skip": 0, "lists": {"optional": false}, "view": {"enum": "number", "recursion": "fail"}}@@);
$parse_Offer = YQL::Udf(AsAtom("Protobuf.Parse"), Void(), Void(), $config_Offer);

~$ /usr/lib/yandex/yql_proto_scheme market.proto.ir.UltraController.proto EnrichedOffer
$config_EnrichedOffer = AsAtom(@@{"name": "Market.UltraControllerServiceData.EnrichedOffer", "meta": "", "format": "protobin", "skip": 0, "lists": {"optional": false}, "view": {"enum": "number", "recursion": "fail"}}@@);
$parse_EnrichedOffer = YQL::Udf(AsAtom("Protobuf.Parse"), Void(), Void(), $config_EnrichedOffer);
```

Now we can use these parsers in YQL request:  
https://yql.yandex-team.ru/Operations/YXKn8RJKfRhUy33EiX_9CoTj9T4EtHiBXL1TVfuyKHo=

## Troubleshooting

* No module named
```
~$ /usr/lib/yandex/yql_proto_scheme market/idx/generation/export-partner-shop-category/proto/service_messages.proto ShopCategoryRec
ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'market.idx.generation.export-partner-shop-category'
```
Check names.  
Make sure that path to .proto file is listed in ```PEERDIR()``` in ya.make file.

* Module has no attribute
```
~$ /usr/lib/yandex/yql_proto_scheme market.proto.ir.UltraController.proto What
AttributeError: module 'market.proto.ir.UltraController_pb2' has no attribute 'What'
```
Check names.
